title: JI’s Muhamad Farooq wins PS- 94 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Jamat e Islami (JI) candidate Muhammad Farooq has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-94, Korangi-II , by securing 23,499 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Abid Jilani, an Independent Candidate, who bagged vote 22,732.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 37.32 %.
